WEBVTT

00:00:08.750 --> 00:00:09.959
[ILULU giggling]

00:00:10.041 --> 00:00:11.709
[DRAGON 202A]
Ilulu...

00:00:11.792 --> 00:00:13.375
--Ilulu.
--[ILULU] Uh?

00:00:13.458 --> 00:00:15.583
[DRAGON 202A] Were you playing
with those humans again?

00:00:15.667 --> 00:00:19.417
[ILULU] Mm-hmm! I love humans
very much! They're so nice!

00:00:19.500 --> 00:00:21.709
[DRAGON 202A]
I see. Then perhaps it is time

00:00:21.792 --> 00:00:25.125
we consider coexisting
with these mortal beings.

00:00:25.208 --> 00:00:26.959
--[ILULU] Mm!
--[DRAGON 202B] Bad news!

00:00:27.041 --> 00:00:29.500
The humans are attacking
the dragon village!

00:00:29.583 --> 00:00:31.208
[DRAGON 202C] This always
happens when we choose

00:00:31.291 --> 00:00:33.041
to stay silent.

00:00:34.208 --> 00:00:37.250
[DRAGON 202C]
Damn humans! They will pay!

00:00:37.333 --> 00:00:39.375
[ILULU]
Where's Mommy and Daddy?

00:00:39.458 --> 00:00:41.458
[DRAGON 202B]
I'm sorry, my dear.

00:00:41.542 --> 00:00:43.959
[ILULU] Does this mean I can't
play with the humans anymore?

00:00:44.041 --> 00:00:45.542
[DRAGON 202B]
Of course it does!

00:00:45.625 --> 00:00:48.917
Those humans are the ones who
took your parents away from you!

00:00:50.083 --> 00:00:52.000
[DRAGON 202C]
They will forever be our enemy!

00:00:52.083 --> 00:00:54.917
We will never come
to an understanding!

00:02:30.458 --> 00:02:33.750
Ah, good. Everyone's asleep.

00:02:35.542 --> 00:02:37.583
[KOBAYASHI] Seeing one of those
up close for the first time

00:02:37.667 --> 00:02:40.083
is traumatic enough
without it being mine.

00:02:40.166 --> 00:02:41.458
--[door latch clicks]
--Ah!

00:02:43.041 --> 00:02:46.250
Hey, there you are,
Miss Kobayashi. Welcome home!

00:02:46.333 --> 00:02:48.542
[giggles] Will you please
let me know next time

00:02:48.625 --> 00:02:49.542
you're going to be late?

00:02:49.625 --> 00:02:51.709
Oh. Yeah. I'm sorry.

00:02:51.792 --> 00:02:55.041
Your face is flushed and sweaty.
Are you feeling okay?

00:02:55.125 --> 00:02:56.417
Huh?!

00:02:56.500 --> 00:02:58.375
[TOHRU] Mm. Maybe you're
catching a cold?

00:02:58.458 --> 00:03:00.583
[KOBAYASHI]
Wah! Don't touch me! I'm fine!

00:03:00.667 --> 00:03:01.959
[TOHRU]
Uh?

00:03:02.041 --> 00:03:03.709
[KOBAYASHI] What the hell?!
Why do I start to sweat

00:03:03.792 --> 00:03:05.917
and almost pass out
whenever I look at her?

00:03:06.000 --> 00:03:07.959
Is it lust? Am I lusting now?!

00:03:08.041 --> 00:03:09.750
After Tohru?!

00:03:09.834 --> 00:03:11.709
Go put your clothes on, please!

00:03:11.792 --> 00:03:13.542
[TOHRU]
Okay?

00:03:13.625 --> 00:03:16.458
[ILULU chuckles]
Kobayashi...

00:03:16.542 --> 00:03:18.709
You can't hide anymore
now that you're a man.

00:03:18.792 --> 00:03:21.417
You'll show everyone
your true colors in no time!

00:03:21.500 --> 00:03:25.500
But I get to see first!
Show me how shallow humans are!

00:03:25.583 --> 00:03:28.041
[KOBAYASHI] That's totally
what this is about.

00:03:28.125 --> 00:03:30.208
I bet Ilulu turned me into
a dude so that I would

00:03:30.291 --> 00:03:33.417
unwittingly display
the worst of humanity.

00:03:33.500 --> 00:03:35.583
I just hope it's over soon.

00:03:37.542 --> 00:03:39.917
[KOBAYASHI] Although,
I have no idea what she's trying

00:03:40.000 --> 00:03:41.417
to get out of me.

00:03:41.500 --> 00:03:44.083
I definitely need
to keep a clear head.

00:03:44.166 --> 00:03:45.750
As a dude. Hmm.

00:03:45.834 --> 00:03:47.417
[alarm ringing]

00:03:47.500 --> 00:03:49.000
[KOBAYASHI groans]

00:03:55.917 --> 00:03:58.291
[KOBAYASHI]
Hey! What are you doing here?!

00:03:59.792 --> 00:04:02.041
I'm snuggling. Good morning.

00:04:02.125 --> 00:04:03.333
But why?

00:04:03.417 --> 00:04:05.250
I was worried you'd
be cold this morning.

00:04:05.333 --> 00:04:08.750
Whoa-kay! I'm warm!
I'm warm and awake!

00:04:08.834 --> 00:04:10.417
Time to start the day.

00:04:12.166 --> 00:04:13.375
[KANNA]
Hmm?

00:04:14.208 --> 00:04:16.083
[KOBAYASHI] I have no idea
how this thing works

00:04:16.166 --> 00:04:18.000
or when it might activate.

00:04:18.083 --> 00:04:21.500
Which is why I'll need to keep
my distance from the others.

00:04:21.583 --> 00:04:23.750
I wonder if this is
something Tohru could fix.

00:04:23.834 --> 00:04:26.000
What?! Miss Kobayashi's a man?!

00:04:26.083 --> 00:04:27.542
What are we waiting for?!

00:04:27.625 --> 00:04:30.792
Let's work on
preserving our species!

00:04:30.875 --> 00:04:32.208
[KOBAYASHI]
Maybe I'll wait.

00:04:32.291 --> 00:04:34.166
[MAN] Okay, it's time to ride
the canoe to adventure!

00:04:34.250 --> 00:04:35.291
[KOBAYASHI]
What are you watching, Kanna?

00:04:35.375 --> 00:04:37.750
[KANNA]
It's called "Clinky Clang."

00:04:39.875 --> 00:04:41.291
[MAN]
