waterfall up ahead!

00:04:51.834 --> 00:04:52.750
[KIDS laughing]

00:04:52.834 --> 00:04:54.750
[TOHRU squeals, giggles]

00:04:54.834 --> 00:04:56.458
[KOBAYASHI] Total disregard
for personal space

00:04:56.542 --> 00:04:58.083
is normal between
female friends!

00:04:58.166 --> 00:04:59.875
It's what we do!
I can handle it.

00:04:59.959 --> 00:05:03.208
I will not allow this penis
to define my instincts!

00:05:03.291 --> 00:05:04.500
[TOHRU]
Save me!

00:05:04.583 --> 00:05:06.375
[KOBAYASHI grunts]
Do not hug me for no reason!

00:05:06.458 --> 00:05:07.792
Kobayashi!

00:05:07.875 --> 00:05:09.250
[KOBAYASHI]
Get up! Please get up!

00:05:09.333 --> 00:05:10.458
[TOHRU]
Miss Kobayashi!

00:05:10.542 --> 00:05:11.709
[KOBAYASHI growls]
What did I tell you

00:05:11.792 --> 00:05:12.959
about random hug attacks?!

00:05:13.041 --> 00:05:13.959
Hi!

00:05:14.041 --> 00:05:15.875
Get out!

00:05:15.959 --> 00:05:17.208
[TOHRU]
Uh...?

00:05:19.709 --> 00:05:22.583
