00:05:22.667 --> 00:05:25.542
That was so close.
I'd forgotten how clingy she is.

00:05:25.625 --> 00:05:27.375
[toilet flushes]

00:05:27.458 --> 00:05:29.333
[KOBAYASHI sighs]
Thank goodness...

00:05:29.417 --> 00:05:32.041
It's finally gotten smaller.

00:05:32.125 --> 00:05:34.125
I figured Ilulu's powers
had been weakened during

00:05:34.208 --> 00:05:36.208
her battle with Tohru.

00:05:38.542 --> 00:05:41.625
[KOBAYASHI] Trying to remember
the factions from Tohru's world.

00:05:41.709 --> 00:05:44.417
