they raise their children

00:05:46.333 --> 00:05:48.250
with the same principles.

00:05:48.333 --> 00:05:52.166
Ilulu grew up that way.
It's the only truth she knows.

00:05:53.750 --> 00:05:55.709
[KOBAYASHI] She can't help
the way she thinks.

00:05:59.375 --> 00:06:01.375
[TOHRU gasps]
Good evening, Miss Kobayashi!

00:06:01.458 --> 00:06:03.959
--Huh?
--Kanna's already asleep.

00:06:04.041 --> 00:06:06.583
Whaddaya say?
How 'bout a night cap?

00:06:06.667 --> 00:06:07.959
[KOBAYASHI chuckles]

