if I wait here?

00:08:20.834 --> 00:08:22.917
[KOBAYASHI]
But why would I do that?

00:08:23.000 --> 00:08:26.250
I might be focusing on
Ilulu a little too much.

00:08:26.333 --> 00:08:29.417
I wonder if it's because I feel
like we could get along somehow?

00:08:31.333 --> 00:08:32.834
[KOBAYASHI] All the dragons
I've met from other worlds

00:08:32.917 --> 00:08:36.250
have been friendly,
so it makes sense.

00:08:36.333 --> 00:08:39.375
