we're not all like that.

00:08:46.542 --> 00:08:48.083
They're willing to believe
there is more to us

00:08:48.166 --> 00:08:50.750
than trouble we cause.

00:08:50.834 --> 00:08:53.875
And that's how
I feel about Tohru, too.

00:08:53.959 --> 00:08:57.291
Which is why it's important
for her to reconcile with Ilulu.

00:08:57.375 --> 00:08:58.625
