00:13:10.291 --> 00:13:12.333
our species, try it!

00:13:12.417 --> 00:13:13.959
[KOBAYASHI] This guy's
making Tohru's father

00:13:14.041 --> 00:13:16.875
seem like a baby garden gecko.

