But...

00:13:18.166 --> 00:13:19.125
[CREMENE]
Hmm?

00:13:20.333 --> 00:13:22.166
[KOBAYASHI]
Humans can be so much worse!

00:13:22.250 --> 00:13:23.333
[ILULU gasps]

00:13:23.417 --> 00:13:26.250
A human who's trying
to protect a dragon?

