--[gasps]
--Well, look who's late.

00:13:42.875 --> 00:13:45.375
[CREMENE whimpers]

00:13:45.458 --> 00:13:46.834
[TOHRU growls]

00:13:46.917 --> 00:13:48.625
[CREMENE gasps]

00:13:48.709 --> 00:13:50.250
[TOHRU snarls]

00:13:50.333 --> 00:13:51.542
[CREMENE]
Ah!

00:13:55.542 --> 00:13:57.041
[ILULU gasps]

00:13:57.125 --> 00:13:59.667
Impossible!
How did you get here?!

00:14:01.041 --> 00:14:02.959
You dare hurt Miss Kobayashi?!

00:14:03.041 --> 00:14:04.792
I... I'm not threatened by you.

00:14:04.875 --> 00:14:07.000
I have reinforcements
waiting to be summoned!

00:14:07.083 --> 00:14:09.125
Lady Elma will
be here any se--

00:14:11.333 --> 00:14:13.625
Choose your words wisely,
you coward.

00:14:13.709 --> 00:14:15.417
Maybe if you beg,
I'll let you keep your soul

00:14:15.500 --> 00:14:17.208
after I crush you.

00:14:17.291 --> 00:14:19.542
Go ahead, beg for
your worthless life!

00:14:19.625 --> 00:14:23.500
--[CREMENE rasping]
--[bones creaking]

00:14:23.583 --> 00:14:25.667
--[ILULU] Uh.
--Ugh...

00:14:25.750 --> 00:14:27.291
[bones crack]

00:14:29.709 --> 00:14:32.625
Um. Did I witness murder?

00:14:32.709 --> 00:14:34.583
[TOHRU] No, I just erased
his memories of this world

00:14:34.667 --> 00:14:37.000
and then sent him back
from whence he came.

00:14:37.083 --> 00:14:39.166
But not before
I punished him, of course.

00:14:39.250 --> 00:14:41.417
Of course.

00:14:41.500 --> 00:14:44.959
[KOBAYASHI] Thank goodness.
Now Ilulu can chill.

00:14:45.041 --> 00:14:47.041
[KOBAYASHI] Oh, gross.
Now that we're okay,

00:14:47.125 --> 00:14:48.792
I'm feeling... Ah!

00:14:48.875 --> 00:14:51.041
[TOHRU]
Ah! Miss Kobayashi?!

00:14:51.125 --> 00:14:54.208
Don't worry, I'll help you out.
[slurps]

00:14:54.291 --> 00:14:56.583
Dragon saliva can
stop bleeding instantly!

00:14:56.667 --> 00:14:58.542
You're just making up
excuses to lick her!

00:14:58.625 --> 00:15:00.333
[TOHRU]
Are you ready, Miss Kobayashi?!

00:15:00.417 --> 00:15:01.583
Lickity, lick-lick-
lick-lick-lick-lick!

00:15:01.667 --> 00:15:04.417
[ILULU]
Your tongue is obscenely long!

00:15:07.959 --> 00:15:09.959
[KOBAYASHI] A functional
member of society is someone

00:15:10.041 --> 00:15:13.500
who diligently obeys the rules
and prioritizes their business

00:15:13.583 --> 00:15:16.291
over their private life.

00:15:16.375 --> 00:15:18.834
I always believed
that's how it was.

00:15:20.333 --> 00:15:22.000
[KOBAYASHI] I was taught
that my purpose in life

00:15:22.083 --> 00:15:26.125
is to fill my role as
a functional member of society.

00:15:26.208 --> 00:15:28.291
Then, the next thing I knew,
I no longer had

00:15:28.375 --> 00:15:30.542
any friends in my private life.

00:15:32.166 --> 00:15:34.458
[KOBAYASHI] And that's when I
met Tohru and when she managed

00:15:34.542 --> 00:15:37.417
to change me for the better.

00:15:37.500 --> 00:15:42.208
I wonder if maybe I was
seeing my old self in Ilulu.

00:15:45.000 --> 00:15:46.083
[KOBAYASHI gasps]

00:15:46.166 --> 00:15:48.333
Miss Kobayashi?
You're finally awake!

00:15:48.417 --> 00:15:49.875
Everything'll be okay.

00:15:49.959 --> 00:15:53.417
Tohru...? Hey there, Kanna.

00:15:53.500 --> 00:15:54.709
Are we in our home?

00:15:54.792 --> 00:15:56.083
We are!

00:15:56.166 --> 00:15:58.542
I brought you back here
and healed your wounds, too!

00:15:58.625 --> 00:16:00.208
[KOBAYASHI]
Where did Ilulu go?

00:16:00.291 --> 00:16:04.000
[TOHRU groans]
She's right there.

00:16:04.083 --> 00:16:05.041
[KOBAYASHI gasps]

00:16:05.125 --> 00:16:07.875
[ILULU whimpering]

00:16:07.959 --> 00:16:10.500
I tried to send her off, but she
wouldn't leave your side!

00:16:10.583 --> 00:16:12.875
I'm glad she finally sees what
we figured out ages ago,

00:16:12.959 --> 00:16:14.667
but it's just a little too late!

00:16:14.750 --> 00:16:15.959
[ILULU]
Kobayashi!

00:16:16.041 --> 00:16:17.125
Wah!

00:16:17.208 --> 00:16:19.500
[ILULU sobs]
Will you please trick me...?

00:16:19.583 --> 00:16:22.125
[KOBAYASHI chuckles]

00:16:22.208 --> 00:16:26.083
--Sure. I'd love to.
--[TOHRU growling]

00:16:31.500 --> 00:16:34.667
[TOHRU whimpering]

00:16:36.291 --> 00:16:37.792
[ANNOUNCER 202A]
Good morning!

00:16:37.875 --> 00:16:41.875
El Niño Miki is here to bring
you today's national weather.

00:16:41.959 --> 00:16:43.917
[KOBAYASHI]
What do we do about that tail?

00:16:44.000 --> 00:16:46.041
I guess those claws
don't retract.

00:16:46.125 --> 00:16:48.542
Is it possible to make
her chest more family-friendly?

00:16:48.625 --> 00:16:49.917
I mean, come on.

00:16:50.000 --> 00:16:52.041
Believe it or not, Ilulu is
already pushing herself

00:16:52.125 --> 00:16:54.959
to maintain a modest size.
If she wasn't,

00:16:55.041 --> 00:16:57.542
I'm not so sure she'd be able
to fit through the door.

00:16:57.625 --> 00:16:59.834
Oh, I bet she could hide her
claws and tail somewhere

00:16:59.917 --> 00:17:01.083
if she tried.

00:17:01.166 --> 00:17:03.750
Wait! Since when can't
she control body parts?!

00:17:03.834 --> 00:17:06.583
All I need is about 5% of that!

00:17:06.667 --> 00:17:08.333
[ILULU]
Kobayashi, Kobayashi.

00:17:08.417 --> 00:17:09.834
Hey, What's up?

00:17:09.917 --> 00:17:12.166
This is where we
eliminate waste, right?

00:17:12.250 --> 00:17:13.291
How does it work?

00:17:13.375 --> 00:17:15.709
Uh. We're doing this?

00:17:15.792 --> 00:17:19.125
Yep. Hop on up there.
And that's basically it.

00:17:19.208 --> 00:17:21.125
[ILULU]
I got it!

00:17:21.208 --> 00:17:23.667
I guess we'll have to
teach her all kinds of things.

00:17:25.542 --> 00:17:29.125
If only I had a talented maid
to help me in times like these.

00:17:29.208 --> 00:17:31.709
I'd probably see them
in a whole new light.

00:17:31.792 --> 00:17:33.458
[TOHRU]
Hmm.

00:17:33.542 --> 00:17:34.750
I'm sorry about this.

00:17:34.834 --> 00:17:37.041
I promise it'll just be
while I'm at work.

00:17:37.125 --> 00:17:38.709
Don't be silly! It's fine!

00:17:38.792 --> 00:17:40.166
It's what you do for
someone when you have

00:17:40.250 --> 00:17:42.000
a special eternal
bond with them!

00:17:42.083 --> 00:17:44.000
I'm not feeling ready
to use the word "eternal."

00:17:44.083 --> 00:17:46.041
[TOHRU]
Okay, bye!

00:17:46.125 --> 00:17:47.959
[TV 202B] Have you been
pumping those muscles, fam?

00:17:48.041 --> 00:17:49.625
When you stop working out,
they start to shrink...

00:17:49.709 --> 00:17:50.959
[TOHRU]
It's weird.

00:17:51.041 --> 00:17:52.875
[ILULU groans]

00:17:52.959 --> 00:17:56.166
[TOHRU] We were trying to
kill each other just days ago.

00:17:56.250 --> 00:17:58.959
[ILULU] There's no way Tohru
would ever forgive a traitor.

00:17:59.041 --> 00:18:01.166
I know she's planning
to eliminate me.

00:18:01.250 --> 00:18:03.625
But I want to spend
more time with Kobayashi.

00:18:03.709 --> 00:18:06.458
And I'm not going
down without a fight.

00:18:06.542 --> 00:18:07.667
There's no fighting.

00:18:07.750 --> 00:18:09.458
[BOTH gasp]

00:18:09.542 --> 00:18:11.000
[sigh]

00:18:11.083 --> 00:18:13.333
[TOHRU]
Here. This is the manual I wrote

00:18:13.417 --> 00:18:15.458
about how to live
your life as a human.

00:18:15.542 --> 00:18:18.125
Rule number A:
change your claws into hands.

00:18:18.208 --> 00:18:20.250
[ILULU]
Hmm? Hmm.

00:18:23.709 --> 00:18:26.125
Ah! Ah...

00:18:27.417 --> 00:18:29.083
[chuckles]

00:18:29.166 --> 00:18:31.667
How is it funny to fail at
the one task you were given.

00:18:31.750 --> 00:18:34.208
Do you suck at everything
or just making hands?

00:18:34.291 --> 00:18:37.500
I can't transform them well.
But I can still read.

00:18:37.583 --> 00:18:39.750
[TOHRU] At least you can hold
some stuff with those things.

00:18:39.834 --> 00:18:41.625
It's a ball of tiny hands! Look!

00:18:41.709 --> 00:18:43.375
[TOHRU]
Ew! Gross!

00:18:45.333 --> 00:18:48.208
[ILULU] "Greetings. Humans
establish communication

00:18:48.291 --> 00:18:49.750
with greetings.

00:18:49.834 --> 00:18:52.709
For now, just repeat whatever
greeting one says to you."

00:18:54.250 --> 00:18:57.250
"Food. Humans will
mostly eat anything,

00:18:57.333 --> 00:18:59.750
but they stubbornly
won't eat dragon meat.

00:18:59.834 --> 00:19:03.500
Currently seeking ways
to get them to change this."

00:19:03.583 --> 00:19:05.667
"Mating. I want to do it"?

00:19:05.750 --> 00:19:07.166
Everything in here is biased!

00:19:07.250 --> 00:19:09.500
It is the whole truth
and nothing but.

00:19:09.583 --> 00:19:11.792
[ILULU] "Clothing. Wearing
clothing similar to what

00:19:11.875 --> 00:19:15.166
other humans wear will
keep you from standing out."

00:19:15.250 --> 00:19:19.333
[ILULU] Hmm? Doesn't look like
you're trying to blend in.

00:19:19.417 --> 00:19:20.333
What?!

00:19:20.417 --> 00:19:21.750
[ILULU]
But whatever you say.

00:19:21.834 --> 00:19:24.458
I can wear human clothes
if we're supposed to.

00:19:24.542 --> 00:19:25.834
We don't have your size here.

00:19:25.917 --> 00:19:26.959
What about Kanna's stuff?

00:19:27.041 --> 00:19:29.041
[TOHRU]
She's even smaller!

00:19:29.125 --> 00:19:31.667
Look, it fits!

00:19:31.750 --> 00:19:34.583
[sighs]
See, what did I tell you?

00:19:34.667 --> 00:19:36.959
Quit making things complicated
and transform your scales

00:19:37.041 --> 00:19:38.041
the way I do!

00:19:38.125 --> 00:19:40.500
I don't have the skills
to do it, okay?

00:19:40.583 --> 00:19:44.083
Sad for you. But I can
lend you something of mine.

00:19:44.166 --> 00:19:46.875
So what do you plan
to contribute here?

00:19:46.959 --> 00:19:48.333
I haven't thought about it.

00:19:48.417 --> 00:19:49.709
Well, what are you good at?

00:19:49.792 --> 00:19:52.000
There has to be
something, right?

00:19:52.083 --> 00:19:54.834
Yeah, I'm sure there is.

00:19:54.917 --> 00:19:56.291
I'm thinking...

00:19:56.375 --> 00:19:57.542
Are you though?

00:19:57.625 --> 00:19:59.250
[ILULU]
Mm-hmm.

00:19:59.333 --> 00:20:01.250
Well, you are welcome
to stay in our home as long

00:20:01.333 --> 00:20:03.375
as you would like until
you make a decision.

00:20:03.458 --> 00:20:05.583
[ILULU] Can you say it
without twitching?

00:20:05.667 --> 00:20:07.417
I know this may
come as a surprise to you,

00:20:07.500 --> 00:20:09.375
Mushroom Mitts, but I am
not particularly thrilled

00:20:09.458 --> 00:20:11.000
to have you here
as a house guest!

00:20:11.083 --> 00:20:12.291
[ILULU]
Not surprised at all.

00:20:12.375 --> 00:20:13.542
[TOHRU]
Think about that humiliating

00:20:13.625 --> 00:20:15.000
grand entrance you made!

00:20:15.083 --> 00:20:17.917
We thought you were some
crazy bloodthirsty berserker.

00:20:18.000 --> 00:20:19.792
[ILULU] Whatever. I was
bored and fighting you

00:20:19.875 --> 00:20:23.917
seemed like fun. Are you trying
to say that's what I look like?!

00:20:24.000 --> 00:20:25.166
All I know is you
better figure out

00:20:25.250 --> 00:20:26.917
what you want your job to be.

00:20:27.000 --> 00:20:29.834
There's a saying that goes,
those who don't work, don't eat.

00:20:29.917 --> 00:20:31.250
What about Kanna?

00:20:31.333 --> 00:20:32.291
[TOHRU]
Kanna can't work.

00:20:32.375 --> 00:20:33.917
She's an elementary
school student.

00:20:34.000 --> 00:20:37.000
Okay, then fine. I'll be an
elementary school student, too!

00:20:37.083 --> 00:20:39.333
You have to be a child
to go to school, dummy.

00:20:39.417 --> 00:20:42.333
And I'm guessing you're about
the same age as me, aren't you?

00:20:42.417 --> 00:20:44.125
Maybe...

00:20:44.208 --> 00:20:45.500
[groans]

00:20:45.583 --> 00:20:47.625
[TOHRU chuckles]

00:20:47.709 --> 00:20:50.458
[TOHRU]
Hurry up and make a choice.

00:20:50.542 --> 00:20:51.750
[KOBAYASHI]
I'm back!

00:20:51.834 --> 00:20:53.500
[TOHRU]
Welcome home!

00:20:53.583 --> 00:20:55.417
What's going on with Ilulu?

00:20:55.500 --> 00:20:58.625
She's thinking about how she
wants to contribute around here.

00:20:58.709 --> 00:21:00.083
[KOBAYASHI]
Hmm...

00:21:00.166 --> 00:21:02.458
[ILULU]
Mm. Mm?

00:21:02.542 --> 00:21:04.000
Whatever you choose
will be great.

00:21:04.083 --> 00:21:06.208
[ILULU]
Mm...

00:21:06.291 --> 00:21:07.542
What's wrong?

00:21:07.625 --> 00:21:10.166
I figured out what I want
to do while I'm here.

00:21:10.250 --> 00:21:12.000
Okay, cool! What is it?

00:21:12.083 --> 00:21:13.750
I want to make babies with you.

00:21:13.834 --> 00:21:15.208
--Huh?!
--[gasps]

00:21:15.291 --> 00:21:17.709
You see, I thought about it
and I'm at the perfect age

00:21:17.792 --> 00:21:20.542
to reproduce and raise
healthy children.

00:21:20.625 --> 00:21:22.667
I'm very lonely from not
having a family and I think

00:21:22.750 --> 00:21:24.333
you're the one to rescue me.

00:21:24.417 --> 00:21:26.625
Kobayashi, I want you
to mate with me!

00:21:26.709 --> 00:21:27.959
You what?!

00:21:28.041 --> 00:21:29.750
I don't know what you're
trying to pull, ma'am,

00:21:29.834 --> 00:21:31.542
but you've crossed
over the line and back!

00:21:31.625 --> 00:21:33.083
Also, we're both female.

00:21:33.166 --> 00:21:34.500
I can give your thing back.

00:21:34.583 --> 00:21:36.917
Don't you dare unless
you want her to use it on me!

00:21:37.000 --> 00:21:38.583
--[snarls]
--Perverts.

00:21:38.667 --> 00:21:40.417
--Yup.
--[TOHRU] I mean it!

00:21:40.500 --> 00:21:42.125
[KOBAYASHI] I'm not trying
to hold on to my purity,

00:21:42.208 --> 00:21:45.125
but I'm also not trying
to get with dragons.

00:21:49.083 --> 00:21:50.500
[KANNA]
Whoa...

00:21:50.583 --> 00:21:54.041
Surprise! I thought
you might like it.

00:21:54.125 --> 00:21:55.875
[giggles]

00:21:55.959 --> 00:21:57.959
[TOHRU groans]

00:23:30.917 --> 00:23:32.500
[KOBAYASHI] Where are you
going to sleep, Ilulu?

00:23:32.583 --> 00:23:34.291
We don't have space
for another bed.

00:23:34.375 --> 00:23:35.625
[ILULU]
What about in here?

00:23:35.709 --> 00:23:37.625
--[KOBAYASHI] The closet?
--[ILULU] It's calming.

00:23:37.709 --> 00:23:39.166
[KOBAYASHI] I mean,
if you're okay with it, sure.

00:23:39.250 --> 00:23:41.166
[ILULU]
Yeah. I like it.

00:23:43.917 --> 00:23:46.542
[CAST]
This week on, "Who's Rotten?"

